subSections.title: Glyph origin
subSections.text:
Unorthodox variant {{Han simp|齒|nocap=y}} ({{l|zh|⿳[[从]][[一]][[从]]}} → {{l|zh|米}}) found in various {{w|Movable type#Metal movable type in China|moveable type}} copies of classical novels.

First attested in 《{{w2|zh|宋元以來俗字譜}}》, a {{w|Variant Chinese character|variant forms}} dictionary compiled in 1930.
